org.voimala.jarzkachess.gamelogic

Class Gameboard

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.voimala.jarzkachess.gamelogic.Gameboard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Gameboard
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents a gameboard, which consists of tiles. In the beginning player 1 (white) starts from the rows 7 and 8. Player 2 (black) starts from the rows 1 and 2. So the gameboard looks like this ABCDEFGH 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
